#!/usr/bin/perl
use XML::DT;

mkdtdskel (@ARGV) #simple huh?

__END__

=encoding utf-8

=head1 NAME

mkdtskel - DTD generator using XML::DT

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  mkdttskel <xmlfile>

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This command tries to infer the DTD structure for a specific XML file;

=head1 SEE ALSO

XML::DT(1), mkdtskel(1) and perl(1)

